</span><span class="linenumber react-syntax-highlighter-line-number" style="display:inline-block;min-width:2.25em;padding-right:1em;text-align:right;user-select:none;color:#6a9955">3</span><span>  use</span><span class="token" style="color:#d4d4d4">:</span><span> </span><span class="token" style="color:#d4d4d4">{</span><span>
