<p class="chakra-text css-en-pr2tx6">There&#x27;s an important note here, Don&#x27;t forget to update images domains in the <code class="chakra-code css-en-4m8w8z" node="[object Object]">next.config.js</code> file.</p>
<ul>
<li class="chakra-text css-en-klhzfh">For code rendering, I use <code class="chakra-code css-en-4m8w8z" node="[object Object]">react-syntax-highlighter</code> and <code class="chakra-code css-en-4m8w8z" node="[object Object]">vscDarkPlus</code> theme like below</li>
